  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our medics, you also have to understand-- our doctors, rather, had been trained to deal with battle casualties.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had never seen anything like that, and in many instances had to improvise as to how to-- how to nurse these women back to health, because if you allowed them to eat too much, they could die from that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And and-- you know, many of their limbs had to be amputated, and to make decisions what-- when to amputate and when not to amputate and how much you allow them to eat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I once spoke to one of the doctors who was there-- this happened not so many years ago.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he wrote us a letter that they had to go strictly by instinct and improvise, because they had not been trained for that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that out of 120 young women who were still liberated, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think more than 30 died yet after that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we also discovered a-- a mass grave outside the town, where-- where in the last days, the SS had still shot a number of-- of the girls on the death march, some of them because they tried to get away and were caught.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we made the German population of the town disinter them and give them a decent burial.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- there are films available of-- of that burial in the town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made the whole population of the town march past the bodies as they were laid out before the-- before burial.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
